    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total showstopper. This car is in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust! It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out and come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
