      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering, preserved in showroom condition. The S54 3.2L inline-six power plant exhibits flawless compression and linear power delivery, with the double-VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal cam phasing. Power is sent through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a rear-mounted limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring a reinforced subframe and a suspension setup that retains its factory-spec damping and bushing elasticity. Finished in a flawless coat with zero orange peel or rock chips, the exterior is matched by an interior where the Nappa leather remains supple and the bolster wear is non-existent. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
