    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true time capsule: this vehicle is in absolute showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero rock chips or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the leather retains its factory-fresh scent and supple texture, with no bolster wear or carpet staining. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships\u2014full maintenance documentation and the original window sticker are included. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives as smoothly as the day it was delivered.",
